---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import { SITE_TITLE } from '../consts';

const pageTitle = "About Emil Mequita";
const pageDescription = "SEO strategist with 10+ years of experience helping businesses rank higher on Google. Enterprise expertise at small business prices.";
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<BaseHead title={`${pageTitle} | ${SITE_TITLE}`} description={pageDescription} />
	</head>
	<body>
		<Header />
		
		<main class="about-page">
			<div class="container">
				<div class="about-content">
					<div class="about-header">
						<img 
							src="https://roastbrief.us/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/0014_Emil.jpeg" 
							alt="Emil Mequita" 
							class="author-photo"
						/>
						<div class="header-text">
							<h1>Hi, I'm Emil Mequita</h1>
							<p class="subtitle">SEO Strategist • 10+ Years Experience • Based in Los Angeles</p>
							<a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/emil-mequita/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="linkedin-link">
								<svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M19 0h-14c-2.761 0-5 2.239-5 5v14c0 2.761 2.239 5 5 5h14c2.762 0 5-2.239 5-5v-14c0-2.761-2.238-5-5-5zm-11 19h-3v-11h3v11zm-1.5-12.268c-.966 0-1.75-.79-1.75-1.764s.784-1.764 1.75-1.764 1.75.79 1.75 1.764-.783 1.764-1.75 1.764zm13.5 12.268h-3v-5.604c0-3.368-4-3.113-4 0v5.604h-3v-11h3v1.765c1.396-2.586 7-2.777 7 2.476v6.759z"/></svg>
								Connect on LinkedIn
							</a>
						</div>
					</div>
					
					<div class="about-story">
						<h2>My Story</h2>
						<p>
							I've spent the last decade helping businesses—from enterprise technology companies to premium e-commerce brands—rank higher on Google and attract more customers organically.
						</p>
						<p>
							My journey started at a digital marketing agency where I cut my teeth on the fundamentals: keyword research, technical SEO, content strategy. Three years later, I moved into healthcare and pharmaceutical marketing, managing SEO for major brands across New York and Los Angeles. That's where I learned to drive real results: I increased keyword indexing by 50% and boosted organic traffic by an average of 30% for every client I touched.
						</p>
						<p>
							From there, I led organic growth for a premium e-commerce brand, building their entire SEO and content strategy from the ground up. Then I ran a client portfolio at a digital agency, where I helped businesses achieve 90% and 140% increases in organic traffic and revenue. Today, I'm directing SEO strategy for a global industrial technology company—but I haven't forgotten where I started.
						</p>
						<p>
							Here's what I've learned after 10+ years and working across healthcare, e-commerce, industrial, and agency environments: <strong>SEO doesn't have to be complicated or expensive.</strong>
						</p>
						<p>
							Small business owners are constantly told they need to hire an agency for $5,000+ per month to see results. That's not true. The strategies that work for Fortune 500 companies work just as well for local businesses—you just need someone to translate enterprise-level tactics into actionable steps you can actually implement.
						</p>
						<p>
							That's why I started YourFriendlySEO. I wanted to give small business owners the same caliber of SEO guidance I provide to global brands, but without the enterprise price tag.
						</p>
					</div>
					
					<div class="about-expertise">
						<h2>What I Do</h2>
						<div class="expertise-grid">
							<div class="expertise-card">
								<div class="expertise-icon">🔍</div>
								<h3>Technical SEO</h3>
								<p>I dig into site architecture, page speed, indexing issues, and Core Web Vitals to make sure Google can crawl and rank your site properly.</p>
							</div>
							
							<div class="expertise-card">
								<div class="expertise-icon">📊</div>
								<h3>GA4 & Analytics</h3>
								<p>I help you track what actually matters—not vanity metrics. Know exactly which pages drive revenue and which need work.</p>
							</div>
							
							<div class="expertise-card">
								<div class="expertise-icon">📝</div>
								<h3>Content Strategy</h3>
								<p>I create content roadmaps that attract your ideal customers and convert them into paying clients—not just traffic for traffic's sake.</p>
							</div>
							
							<div class="expertise-card">
								<div class="expertise-icon">🎯</div>
								<h3>Keyword Research</h3>
								<p>I find the keywords your competitors are missing—the ones with high buyer intent and lower competition.</p>
							</div>
							
							<div class="expertise-card">
								<div class="expertise-icon">🛒</div>
								<h3>E-commerce SEO</h3>
								<p>From product pages to category optimization, I've helped e-commerce brands scale organic revenue by triple digits.</p>
							</div>
							
							<div class="expertise-card">
								<div class="expertise-icon">🤖</div>
								<h3>AI + Search</h3>
								<p>I stay ahead of how AI is changing search—from ChatGPT to Google's AI Overviews—so your strategy stays relevant.</p>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>
					
					<div class="about-philosophy">
						<h2>My Philosophy</h2>
						<p>
							I believe SEO should be <strong>practical, transparent, and results-focused.</strong> No jargon. No vague promises. Just clear strategies that work.
						</p>
						<p>
							When you work with me—whether through my guides, templates, or 1-on-1 consultations—you get the same level of strategic thinking I bring to enterprise clients. The difference is I package it in a way that makes sense for small businesses with limited time and budget.
						</p>
						<p>
							You'll walk away knowing exactly what to do, why it matters, and how to measure success. No confusion. No fluff. Just actionable SEO.
						</p>
					</div>
					
					<div class="about-cta">
						<h2>Let's Work Together</h2>
						<p>
							If you're serious about ranking higher and attracting more customers organically, I can help.
						</p>
						<div class="cta-buttons">
							<a href="/consultation" class="btn btn-primary btn-large">Book a Strategy Session</a>
							<a href="/blog" class="btn btn-secondary btn-large">Read Free Guides</a>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</main>
		
		<Footer />
	</body>
</html>

<style>
	.about-page {
		background-color: var(--color-white);
	}
	
	.about-content {
		max-width: var(--container-md);
		margin: 0 auto;
		padding: var(--space-12) var(--space-4) var(--space-20);
	}
	
	/* Header Section */
	.about-header {
		display: flex;
		gap: var(--space-8);
		align-items: center;
		margin-bottom: var(--space-16);
		padding-bottom: var(--space-12);
		border-bottom: 2px solid var(--color-gray-200);
	}
	
	.author-photo {
		width: 200px;
		height: 200px;
		border-radius: var(--radius-full);
		object-fit: cover;
		border: 4px solid var(--color-accent);
		box-shadow: var(--shadow-xl);
		flex-shrink: 0;
	}
	
	.header-text h1 {
		font-size: var(--font-size-5xl);
		color: var(--color-primary);
		margin-bottom: var(--space-3);
	}
	
	.subtitle {
		font-size: var(--font-size-xl);
		color: var(--color-gray-600);
		margin-bottom: var(--space-6);
	}
	
	.linkedin-link {
		display: inline-flex;
		align-items: center;
		gap: var(--space-2);
		padding: var(--space-3) var(--space-5);
		background-color: var(--color-primary);
		color: var(--color-white);
		text-decoration: none;
		font-weight: var(--font-weight-semibold);
		border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
		transition: all 0.2s ease;
	}
	
	.linkedin-link:hover {
		background-color: var(--color-primary-light);
		transform: translateY(-2px);
		box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg);
		text-decoration: none;
	}
	
	.linkedin-link svg {
		flex-shrink: 0;
	}
	
	/* Story Section */
	.about-story {
		margin-bottom: var(--space-16);
	}
	
	.about-story h2 {
		font-size: var(--font-size-4xl);
		color: var(--color-primary);
		margin-bottom: var(--space-6);
	}
	
	.about-story p {
		font-size: var(--font-size-lg);
		line-height: var(--line-height-relaxed);
		color: var(--color-gray-700);
		margin-bottom: var(--space-6);
	}
	
	.about-story p strong {
		color: var(--color-primary);
	}
	
	/* Expertise Section */
	.about-expertise {
		margin-bottom: var(--space-16);
		padding: var(--space-12);
		background-color: var(--color-gray-50);
		border-radius: var(--radius-2xl);
	}
	
	.about-expertise h2 {
		font-size: var(--font-size-4xl);
		color: var(--color-primary);
		margin-bottom: var(--space-10);
		text-align: center;
	}
	
	.expertise-grid {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
		gap: var(--space-8);
	}
	
	.expertise-card {
		background-color: var(--color-white);
		padding: var(--space-6);
		border-radius: var(--radius-xl);
		border: 2px solid var(--color-gray-200);
		transition: all 0.2s ease;
	}
	
	.expertise-card:hover {
		border-color: var(--color-accent);
		box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg);
		transform: translateY(-2px);
	}
	
	.expertise-icon {
		font-size: 40px;
		margin-bottom: var(--space-4);
	}
	
	.expertise-card h3 {
		font-size: var(--font-size-xl);
		color: var(--color-primary);
		margin-bottom: var(--space-3);
	}
	
	.expertise-card p {
		font-size: var(--font-size-base);
		color: var(--color-gray-600);
		line-height: var(--line-height-relaxed);
		margin: 0;
	}
	
	/* Philosophy Section */
	.about-philosophy {
		margin-bottom: var(--space-16);
	}
	
	.about-philosophy h2 {
		font-size: var(--font-size-4xl);
		color: var(--color-primary);
		margin-bottom: var(--space-6);
	}
	
	.about-philosophy p {
		font-size: var(--font-size-lg);
		line-height: var(--line-height-relaxed);
		color: var(--color-gray-700);
		margin-bottom: var(--space-6);
	}
	
	.about-philosophy p strong {
		color: var(--color-primary);
	}
	
	/* CTA Section */
	.about-cta {
		background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--color-primary) 0%, var(--color-primary-light) 100%);
		padding: var(--space-12);
		border-radius: var(--radius-2xl);
		text-align: center;
		color: var(--color-white);
	}
	
	.about-cta h2 {
		font-size: var(--font-size-4xl);
		color: var(--color-white);
		margin-bottom: var(--space-4);
	}
	
	.about-cta p {
		font-size: var(--font-size-xl);
		color: var(--color-gray-200);
		margin-bottom: var(--space-8);
	}
	
	.cta-buttons {
		display: flex;
		gap: var(--space-4);
		justify-content: center;
		flex-wrap: wrap;
	}
	
	/* Responsive */
	@media (max-width: 768px) {
		.about-header {
			flex-direction: column;
			text-align: center;
		}
		
		.author-photo {
			width: 150px;
			height: 150px;
		}
		
		.header-text h1 {
			font-size: var(--font-size-3xl);
		}
		
		.expertise-grid {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
		}
		
		.about-story h2,
		.about-expertise h2,
		.about-philosophy h2,
		.about-cta h2 {
			font-size: var(--font-size-3xl);
		}
		
		.cta-buttons {
			flex-direction: column;
		}
		
		.cta-buttons .btn {
			width: 100%;
		}
	}
</style>
